## PriorityQueue class

A PriorityQueue is like a [Queue](./promizr.queue.md) but executes items in priority order.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export default class PriorityQueue<T, U> extends Queue<T, U> 
```
<b>Extends:</b> Queue&lt;T, U&gt;
